messages.message: Hi team, on prod (https://www.instabase.com/apps/text-editor/ganan.prabaharan/reusable_items/fs/Instabase%20Drive/export_to_excel_reduce_udf.py?) the save button for changing the tab size in Settings for Text-Editor doesn’t seem to work
Thanks for reporting @Ganan Prabaharan. Are you aware of whether this is a recent regression? Or you just happened to click on it and notice it this time.
Yeah it was my first time trying to change tab size, so not sure if it’s a recent regression

Got it, my guess is it’s been around for a veryyy long time. i’ll track it on the Jira backlog, but likely won’t fix it anytime soon. fyi @Xindi Xu in case you’re aware of this already and know what’s happening.
